01:29:25,966 --> 01:29:28,802
Well, maybe Clarence
would like to see you alone.

1154
01:29:30,512 --> 01:29:32,138
All right.

1155
01:29:41,856 --> 01:29:44,776
Call the Victory Committee
and tell them I'll be at the camp.

1156
01:29:44,943 --> 01:29:47,153
