01:37:48,260 --> 01:37:51,554
Oh, hello, Clarence.
I hope you haven't been waiting long.

1248
01:37:51,805 --> 01:37:54,766
- Well, I...
- What did you say?

1249
01:37:55,016 --> 01:37:57,394
I didn't say anything.
